 Television: The new United Paramount Network is said to be near a deal with 
"Mighty Morphin Power Rangers" creator Saban Entertainment to provide the new 
network with new children's programming starting next fall. News of the 
alliance circulated at United Paramount's affiliates gathering last week, where 
