<HEADLINE>
<P>
COUNTYWIDE FOCUS: METROLINK TO OFFER SPECIAL HOLIDAY TRAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By SARA CATANIA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In the spirit of holiday cheer -- and in the hope of attracting a few new 
riders -- Metrolink will offer a special weekend train Dec. 17. 
</P>
<P>
 The train will run from Oxnard to Los Angeles in the morning and return in 
late afternoon, with stops at all 10 Metrolink stations along the route, 
including Camarillo, Moorpark and Simi Valley. 
</P>
<P>
 A discount ticket is available in advance for $5. 
</P>
<P>
 Children under 6 travel free with a paying adult. 
</P>
<P>
 For tickets and schedules, call Metrolink at (800) 371-LINK or the Ventura 
County Transportation Commission at (800) 438-1112. SARA CATANIA 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120694-0073 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 105296 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
