<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY ALMANAC 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 It's not exactly Boston, but Fullerton is home to quite a few institutions of 
higher learning. 
</P>
<P>
 City officials estimate that more than 47,000 students pursue higher learning, 
from junior college to law school, in the city. 03,42,13,10 Established 
Students Cal State Fullerton 1959 25,000 Fullerton College 1913 20,000 Pacific 
Christian College 1928 568 Southern California College of Optometry 1904 385 
Western State University Law School 1966 1,200 Today 
</P>
<P>
 Your Christmas tradition might include lots of trips to the shopping mall. But 
each culture has its own way of celebrating the holidays. 
</P>
<P>
 The Irvine Barclay Theatre will present a performance today titled "Christmas 
Traditions Around the World." The program will be performed by the Irvine 
Ballet Company. 
</P>
<P>
 The theater is at 4242 Campus Drive in Irvine. Tickets to the show are from 
$10 to $12. The performance will start at 7:30 p.m. For more information, call 
(714) 854-4646. 
