<DOCNO> LA120694-0186 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 105409 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 6, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Page 19 
