<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120694-0238 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 105461 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 6, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
