<DATE>
<P>
December 6, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Special Section; Part V; Page 1; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
